data.description: Nestled in a sought-after neighborhood, this charming one-story, single-family home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms , home study/office, perfect for modern living. The heart of the home, a fully remodeled kitchen, features stunning silestone countertops and recent stainless appliances (2022), sure to delight any culinary enthusiast. Comfort is assured with a recently updated AC unit (2021), and peace of mind is provided by the roof, replaced in 2018. This home includes a spacious 2-car garage. It's conveniently located within the acclaimed Cy-Fair School District and offers easy access to Hwy 290, making commuting a breeze. Fully fenced backyard offers space and a 10x20' concrete patio. This delightful residence is an ideal blend of comfort, convenience, and contemporary living. Need to move quick? This seller is able to offer a 7-14 day close
